    <item>
      <title>Información y Visión</title>
      <link>https://Wz676.github.io/Eco.voces/informacion/</link>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Mar 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>https://Wz676.github.io/Eco.voces/informacion/</guid>
      <description>&lt;div style=&#34;max-width: 1200px; margin: 50px auto; padding: 0 20px;&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;h1 style=&#34;text-align: center; margin-bottom: 3rem;&#34;&gt;Nuestra Misión Ecológica&lt;/h1&gt;&#xA;&lt;style&gt;&#xA;    .eco-story { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; align-items: center; margin: 3rem 0; gap: 3rem; }&#xA;     &#xA;    .eco-story-img { flex: 1 1 300px; border-radius: 15px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.15); }&#xA;    .eco-story-img img { width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; object-fit: cover; transition: transform 0.3s ease; }&#xA;    .eco-story-img img:hover { transform: scale(1.05); }  &#xA;    &#xA;     &#xA;    .eco-story-text { flex: 1 1 300px; text-align: left; }&#xA;    .eco-story-text h3 { margin-top: 0; font-size: 2rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; }&#xA;    .eco-story-text p { font-size: 1.1rem; line-height: 1.8; opacity: 0.8; }&#xA;  &lt;/style&gt;&#xA;  &#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;eco-story&#34; data-aos=&#34;fade-up&#34; &gt;&#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;eco-story-text&#34;&gt;&#xA;      &lt;h3&gt;¿Por qué Reciclar?&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;      &lt;p&gt;&#xA;  Aquí explicamos la importancia del reciclaje dentro de la Universidad Bicentenaria de Aragua. Los desechos tecnológicos y plásticos son un problema creciente.&#xA;  &lt;/p&gt;</description>
      
    </item>
    
    <item>
      <title>Zona de Interacción</title>
      <link>https://Wz676.github.io/Eco.voces/interactuar/</link>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Mar 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>https://Wz676.github.io/Eco.voces/interactuar/</guid>
      <description>&lt;div style=&#34;text-align: center; margin-top: 50px; margin-bottom: 40px;&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;h1 style=&#34;font-size: 2.5rem;&#34;&gt;🎮 Zona de Interacción&lt;/h1&gt;&#xA;  &lt;p style=&#34;font-size: 1.2rem; opacity: 0.8;&#34;&gt;Elige tu actividad y ayúdanos a mejorar el campus de la UBA.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;style&gt;&#xA;    .action-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr)); gap: 30px; max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto 50px auto; padding: 0 20px; }&#xA;    .action-card { background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6); backdrop-filter: blur(10px); border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4); border-radius: 20px; padding: 40px 20px; text-align: center; cursor: pointer; box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.05); transition: all 0.3s; }&#xA;    .action-card:hover { transform: translateY(-10px); box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.2); border-color: #10b981; }&#xA;    .card-icon { font-size: 4rem; margin-bottom: 15px; }&#xA;    .card-title { font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 10px; color: #1f2937; }&#xA;    .card-desc { color: #6b7280; font-size: 0.95rem; }&#xA;    .dark .action-card { background: rgba(30, 41, 59, 0.6); border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1); }&#xA;    .dark .card-title { color: #f3f4f6; } .dark .card-desc { color: #9ca3af; }&#xA;  &#xA;     &#xA;    .modal-overlay { display: none; position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%; background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6); backdrop-filter: blur(8px); z-index: 9999; align-items: center; justify-content: center; opacity: 0; transition: opacity 0.3s ease; }&#xA;    .modal-content { background: white; width: 90%; max-width: 800px; height: 85vh; border-radius: 20px; position: relative; transform: scale(0.9); transition: transform 0.3s; box-shadow: 0 25px 50px rgba(0,0,0,0.3); display: flex; flex-direction: column; overflow: hidden; }&#xA;    .dark .modal-content { background: #1e293b; border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1); }&#xA;    .close-btn { position: absolute; top: 15px; right: 20px; font-size: 2.5rem; color: #6b7280; cursor: pointer; z-index: 10; line-height: 1; }&#xA;    .close-btn:hover { color: #ef4444; }&#xA;    .modal-overlay.active { display: flex; opacity: 1; }&#xA;    .modal-overlay.active .modal-content { transform: scale(1); }&#xA;  &lt;/style&gt;&#xA;  &#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;action-grid&#34; data-aos=&#34;fade-up&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;action-card&#34; onclick=&#34;openModal(&#39;survey-modal&#39;)&#34;&gt;&#xA;      &lt;div class=&#34;card-icon&#34;&gt;📊&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;      &lt;div class=&#34;card-title&#34;&gt;Encuesta de Sostenibilidad&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;      &lt;div class=&#34;card-desc&#34;&gt;Toma 1 minuto. Danos tu opinión sobre los hábitos de reciclaje en la universidad.&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;action-card&#34; onclick=&#34;alert(&#39;El juego Eco.Clasificador se está programando... ¡Vuelve pronto! 🛠️&#39;)&#34;&gt;&#xA;      &lt;div class=&#34;card-icon&#34;&gt;🕹️&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;      &lt;div class=&#34;card-title&#34;&gt;Juego: Eco.Clasificador&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;      &lt;div class=&#34;card-desc&#34;&gt;Pon a prueba tus reflejos separando la basura. ¡Gana puntos y salva el planeta!&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;  &#xA;  &lt;div id=&#34;survey-modal&#34; class=&#34;modal-overlay&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;modal-content&#34;&gt;&#xA;      &lt;span class=&#34;close-btn&#34; onclick=&#34;closeModal(&#39;survey-modal&#39;)&#34;&gt;&amp;times;&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;      &lt;iframe src=&#34;https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSdMo5gMDrIlG5GDXIBjEucrJTXX3HZ7IXGpszNe3yhY9JCX8w/viewform?embedded=true&#34; width=&#34;100%&#34; height=&#34;100%&#34; frameborder=&#34;0&#34; marginheight=&#34;0&#34; marginwidth=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;border-radius: 20px; background: transparent;&#34;&gt;Cargando…&lt;/iframe&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;  &#xA;  &lt;script&gt;&#xA;    function openModal(modalId) {&#xA;      document.getElementById(modalId).classList.add(&#39;active&#39;);&#xA;      document.body.style.overflow = &#39;hidden&#39;;&#xA;    }&#xA;    function closeModal(modalId) {&#xA;      document.getElementById(modalId).classList.remove(&#39;active&#39;);&#xA;      document.body.style.overflow = &#39;auto&#39;;&#xA;    }&#xA;    window.onclick = function(event) {&#xA;      if (event.target.classList.contains(&#39;modal-overlay&#39;)) {&#xA;        event.target.classList.remove(&#39;active&#39;);&#xA;        document.body.style.overflow = &#39;auto&#39;;&#xA;      }&#xA;    }&#xA;  &lt;/script&gt;&#xA;&lt;link href=&#34;https://unpkg.com/aos@2.3.1/dist/aos.css&#34; rel=&#34;stylesheet&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;script src=&#34;https://unpkg.com/aos@2.3.1/dist/aos.js&#34;&gt;&lt;/script&gt;&#xA;&lt;script&gt;setTimeout(function(){ AOS.init({ duration: 800, once: true }); }, 100);&lt;/script&gt;</description>
      
